info.pavie.opennetworkmap.controller.standardizer

Interface NetworkStandardizer

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BusLineStandardizer, DetailedElectricityStandardizer, ElectricityStandardizer, SubwayStandardizer

    public interface NetworkStandardizer
    A network standardizer allows to transform a lot of OSM data into a standard Network. It depends of the elements you want to keep, for example keep only bus lines or water pipelines. A class which implements this interface is able to give you a standard network for your purpose.
